formulas.name: DefaultUpliftPercent
formulas.expression: IF({!Auto_Renewal_Escalation} = "1", 1, IF({!Auto_Renewal_Escalation} = "2", 2, IF({!Auto_Renewal_Escalation} = "3", 3, IF({!Auto_Renewal_Escalation} = "4", 4, IF({!Auto_Renewal_Escalation} = "5", 5, IF({!Auto_Renewal_Escalation} = "6", 6, IF({!Auto_Renewal_Escalation} = "7", 7, IF({!Auto_Renewal_Escalation} = "8", 8, IF({!Auto_Renewal_Escalation} = "9", 9, IF({!Auto_Renewal_Escalation} = "10", 10, NULL ))))))))))
